<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="151">
Konow described 
<taxonomicName family="Tenthredinidae" genus="D." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="D. schmidti" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" rank="species" species="schmidti">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">D. schmidti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a new species only because 
<taxonomicName family="Tenthredinidae" genus="D." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="D. liogaster" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" rank="species" species="liogaster">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">D. liogaster</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Thomson was not known to him at the time. Later 
<taxonomicName family="Tenthredinidae" genus="D." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="D. schmidti" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" rank="species" species="schmidti">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">D. schmidti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was treated as a variety of 
<taxonomicName family="Tenthredinidae" genus="D." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="D. liogaster" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" rank="species" species="liogaster">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">D. liogaster</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Konow, FW" journalOrPublisher="Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" pagination="241 - 255" refId="B89" refString="Konow, FW, 1890b. Catalogus Tenthredinidarum Europae. (Hymenopterorum XVI familiae.). Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift 1890 (2): 241 - 255" title="Catalogus Tenthredinidarum Europae. (Hymenopterorum XVI familiae.)." volume="1890" year="1890 b">Konow (1890b</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Konow, FW" journalOrPublisher="Entomologisches Nachrichtenblatt (Vienna, Austria)" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" pagination="225 - 245" refId="B96" refString="Konow, FW, 1898. Neuer Beitrag zur Synonymie der Chalastogastra. Entomologisches Nachrichtenblatt (Vienna, Austria) 24 (15-16): 225 - 245" title="Neuer Beitrag zur Synonymie der Chalastogastra." volume="24" year="1898">1898</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Konow, FW" journalOrPublisher="Genera Insectorum" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" pagination="1 - 176" refId="B99" refString="Konow, FW, 1905b. Hymenoptera. Fam. Tenthredinidae. Genera Insectorum 29: 1 - 176" title="Hymenoptera. Fam. Tenthredinidae." volume="29" year="1905 b">1905b</bibRefCitation>
) and synonymized with it by 
<bibRefCitation author="Enslin, E" journalOrPublisher="Izvestija Stavropol'skogo Entomologiceskogo Obscestva" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" refId="B42" refString="Enslin, E, 1913. Die Tenthredinoidea Mitteleuropas II. Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift (Beiheft 2): 99-202." title="Die Tenthredinoidea Mitteleuropas II. Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift (Beiheft 2): 99 - 202." year="1913">Enslin (1913)</bibRefCitation>
. The lectotype female was wrongly interpreted as a holotype by 
<bibRefCitation author="Oehlke, J" journalOrPublisher="Beitraege zur Entomologie" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" pagination="363 - 420" refId="B139" refString="Oehlke, J, Wudowenz, J, 1984. Katalog der in den Sammlungen der Abteilung Taxonomie der Insekten des Institutes fuer Pflanzenschutzforschung, Bereich Eberswalde (ehemals Deutsches Entomologisches Institut), aufbewahrten Typen - XXII (Hymenoptera: Symphyta). Beitraege zur Entomologie 34 (2): 363 - 420" title="Katalog der in den Sammlungen der Abteilung Taxonomie der Insekten des Institutes fuer Pflanzenschutzforschung, Bereich Eberswalde (ehemals Deutsches Entomologisches Institut), aufbewahrten Typen - XXII (Hymenoptera: Symphyta)." volume="34" year="1984">Oehlke and Wudowenz (1984)</bibRefCitation>
and followed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Heidemaa, M" journalOrPublisher="Entomologica Scandinavica" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" refId="B65" refString="Heidemaa, M, 2004. Systematic studies on sawflies of the genera Dolerus, Empria, and Caliroa (Hymenoptera: Tenthredinidae). Dissertationes Biologicae Universitatis Tartuensis, Tartu, 1-167. [nomenclatural acts unavailable because of a disclaimer]" title="Systematic studies on sawflies of the genera Dolerus, Empria, and Caliroa (Hymenoptera: Tenthredinidae). Dissertationes Biologicae Universitatis Tartuensis, Tartu, 1 - 167. [nomenclatural acts unavailable because of a disclaimer]" year="2004">Heidemaa (2004)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
